05.05.2018
good practice:
* Set font-size to 62.5% in html
* Use box-sizing: border-box; at body tag and than ingerit it in *,::after,::before selectors
* The 7-1 Pattern (The 7 folders) 7 different folders for partials and 1 main file that will import other files into and compile stylesheet
    base/           // -> basic project definitions
    components/     // -> one file for each component
    layout/         // -> overall layout of the project
    pages/          // -> styles for specific pages of the project
    themes/         // -> styles fot diferent visual themes
    abstract/       // -> codet that doesent output any css, such as variables and mixins
    vendors/        // -> 3th party css

09.05.2018
Atribute selector []
[alt=logo]     // select selecotrs with atribute alt equal logo
[class^="col"] // select class starts with 'col'
[class=$"col"]  // select class ends with 'col'
[class*="col"]                // contain

11.05.2018
When we hover composition than select photo that is not hover
css: composition:hover composition__photo:not(:hover) { }
scss: &:hover &__photo:not(:hover) { }

